<template>
  <view class="page">
    <view class="bg-glow glow-purple"></view>
    <view class="bg-glow glow-blue"></view>
    <view class="bg-glow glow-pink"></view>
    <view class="sky-star star-a"></view>
    <view class="sky-star star-b"></view>
    <view class="sky-star star-c"></view>
    <view class="sky-star star-d"></view>
    <view class="sky-star star-e"></view>
    <view class="sky-star star-f"></view>
    <view class="sky-star star-g"></view>
    <view class="sky-star star-h"></view>
    <view class="sky-star star-i"></view>
    <view class="sky-star star-j"></view>
    <view class="sky-star star-k"></view>
    <view class="sky-star star-l"></view>
    <scroll-view class="scroll-area" scroll-y="true">
      <view class="hero-block">
        <view class="hero-copy">
          <text class="hero-brand">微憩星球</text>
          <text class="hero-title">轻轻守护，从 10 秒开始</text>
          <text class="hero-subtitle">它会观察你的使用节奏，在合适的时候提醒你眨眨眼、松松肩、慢慢呼吸。</text>
        </view>
        <view class="hero-planet-card">
          <view class="hero-orbit"></view>
          <view class="hero-icon-wrap">
            <text class="hero-icon">◐</text>
          </view>
          <text class="hero-chip">不说教 · 不打扰</text>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="value-block">
        <text class="block-title">AI 健康大脑在做什么</text>
        <text class="block-subtitle">不是催你打卡，而是把使用节奏、完成反馈和健康状态一起看懂。</text>
        <view class="ai-core-card">
          <view class="ai-core-icon">
            <text class="ai-core-icon-text">AI</text>
          </view>
          <view class="ai-core-copy">
            <text class="ai-core-title">先判断，再轻轻提醒</text>
            <text class="ai-core-text">本地规则引擎实时看连续使用时长，推荐算法选择当下更适合的护眼、体态或呼吸动作。</text>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class="value-grid">
          <view class="value-card">
            <text class="value-icon value-icon-blue">◌</text>
            <text class="value-title">解决忘休息</text>
            <text class="value-text">刷久了才提醒，不靠你自己想起来</text>
          </view>
          <view class="value-card value-card-even">
            <text class="value-icon value-icon-purple">✦</text>
            <text class="value-title">推荐做什么</text>
            <text class="value-text">按时间段和历史完成情况选微动作</text>
          </view>
          <view class="value-card">
            <text class="value-icon value-icon-pink">⌁</text>
            <text class="value-title">AI 小结报告</text>
            <text class="value-text">每日一句话、每周建议和下周小目标</text>
          </view>
          <view class="value-card value-card-even">
            <text class="value-icon value-icon-blue">◐</text>
            <text class="value-title">越用越懂你</text>
            <text class="value-text">完成、跳过、忙一下，都会帮助调节频率</text>
          </view>
        </view>
        <text class="value-privacy">只识别你正在使用哪个 App 和连续用了多久，不读取聊天内容、密码或屏幕文字。</text>
      </view>

      <view class="focus-block">
        <text class="block-title">选择守护重点</text>
        <text class="block-subtitle">之后可以随时修改，现在先选一个你最想照顾的方向。</text>
        <view class="focus-grid">
          <view class="focus-card" :class="selectedFocus === 'eye' ? 'focus-active' : ''" @tap="selectFocus('eye')">
            <text class="focus-icon">◐</text>
            <text class="focus-title">护眼优先</text>
          </view>
          <view class="focus-card" :class="selectedFocus === 'posture' ? 'focus-active' : ''" @tap="selectFocus('posture')">
            <text class="focus-icon">◌</text>
            <text class="focus-title">肩颈优先</text>
          </view>
          <view class="focus-card" :class="selectedFocus === 'breath' ? 'focus-active' : ''" @tap="selectFocus('breath')">
            <text class="focus-icon">⌁</text>
            <text class="focus-title">减压呼吸</text>
          </view>
          <view class="focus-card" :class="selectedFocus === 'balance' ? 'focus-active' : ''" @tap="selectFocus('balance')">
            <text class="focus-icon">✧</text>
            <text class="focus-title">均衡发展</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="steps-block">
        <text class="block-title">开启轻轻守护</text>
        <text class="block-subtitle">权限只用于识别 App 和连续使用时长，不读取聊天内容、密码或屏幕文字。</text>
        <view class="step-card">
          <view class="step-num-wrap step-num-1">
            <text class="step-num">1</text>
          </view>
          <view class="step-content">
            <text class="step-title">开启使用情况权限</text>
            <text class="step-desc">用来检测你正在使用哪个 App，以及连续使用了多久</text>
            <view class="step-status-row">
              <text class="step-status" :class="usageEnabled ? 'step-status-on' : 'step-status-off'">
                {{ usageEnabled ? '✅ 已开启' : '⚪ 未开启' }}
              </text>
              <view v-if="!usageEnabled" class="step-action-btn" @tap="openUsageAccess">
                <text class="step-action-btn-text">立即开启</text>
              </view>
            </view>
          </view>
        </view>

        <view class="step-card">
          <view class="step-num-wrap step-num-2">
            <text class="step-num">2</text>
          </view>
          <view class="step-content">
            <text class="step-title">开启悬浮窗权限</text>
            <text class="step-desc">用来在其他 App 上方显示微动作提醒</text>
            <view class="step-status-row">
              <text class="step-status" :class="overlayEnabled ? 'step-status-on' : 'step-status-off'">
                {{ overlayEnabled ? '✅ 已开启' : '⚪ 未开启' }}
              </text>
              <view v-if="!overlayEnabled" class="step-action-btn" @tap="openOverlay">
                <text class="step-action-btn-text">立即开启</text>
              </view>
            </view>
          </view>
        </view>

        <view class="step-card step-card-info">
          <view class="step-num-wrap step-num-3">
            <text class="step-num">3</text>
          </view>
          <view class="step-content">
            <text class="step-title">后台守护</text>
            <text class="step-desc">用来保持提醒服务稳定运行，不打扰你的正常使用</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="demo-block">
        <text class="block-title">演示一次</text>
        <text class="block-subtitle">假设你刷屏久了一点，小星球会这样提醒你。</text>
        <view class="demo-card">
          <view class="demo-planet">
            <text class="demo-planet-text">◐</text>
          </view>
          <view class="demo-copy">
            <text class="demo-title">星球信号提醒</text>
            <text class="demo-text">检测到眼睛电量有点低，要不要眨眼 10 秒？</text>
          </view>
          <view class="demo-action" @tap="startDemo">
            <text class="demo-action-text">{{ demoStarted ? '演示中' : '好啊' }}</text>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view v-if="demoStarted" class="demo-flow">
          <view class="demo-stage">
            <view class="demo-stage-planet">
              <view class="demo-stage-orbit"></view>
              <text class="demo-stage-icon">◐</text>
            </view>
            <view class="demo-stage-copy">
              <text class="demo-stage-title">进入 10 秒微动作</text>
              <text class="demo-stage-text">真实使用时会进入动作页，显示引导文案、倒计时和跳过按钮。</text>
            </view>
          </view>
          <view class="demo-progress">
            <view class="demo-progress-fill"></view>
          </view>
          <view class="demo-steps">
            <view class="demo-step">
              <text class="demo-step-num">1</text>
              <text class="demo-step-text">收到提醒</text>
            </view>
            <view class="demo-step">
              <text class="demo-step-num">2</text>
              <text class="demo-step-text">点“好啊”</text>
            </view>
            <view class="demo-step">
              <text class="demo-step-num">3</text>
              <text class="demo-step-text">跟着倒计时做完</text>
            </view>
          </view>
          <text class="demo-result">完成后，小星球会点亮一次，并把这次照顾记录进健康轨迹。</text>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="cta-block">
